ygData.messageBody:
It had an axe graphic I was there and he charmed him maybe a week ago, weekend
sometime. The person who looted it never mentioned it not being the exe axe and
this is the first time I have ever heard of a critter not having a graphic for a
weapon it has, it was also my second time in lower guk. As for the pet thing it
may have been a fluke I don't know as I don't play anything that uses pets so I
can't tell you, but I did clearly see from the executioner "guarding with my
life oh splendid one" Mersinaz even laughed because we didn't know what he was
doing at first. AND WHEN YOU ARE GOING TO INSULT ME AT LEAST GET THE NAME
SPELLED RIGHT!!!! As for the pets I am pretty sure the guy who has the
information attained it though illegal methods because he seems very greasy and
probably won't ever tell me but I am gonna try and when I get it the person who
doubted me doesn't have to use it

Efrieum
35 warrior
